SUMMARY:37th LD Memberwide Endorsement Forum
DESCRIPTION:A candidate has applied for Seattle DSA’s endorsement for the 37th Legislative District Washington State House races – Jaelynn Scott is running for the open seat! Bring your questions for Jaelynn to the Memberwide Endorsement Forum and take advantage of this excellent chance to learn more about the candidate and the race before we vote on whether to endorse at March Local Convention. Relevant documents: \nJaelynn Scott Questionnaire | Q&A Transcript \nLet’s show up\, stay engaged\, and participate in making an informed decision. RSVP to receive an update when a location is determined! \nSolidarity\, \nSeattle DSA Electoral Working Group
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/37th-ld-memberwide-endorsement-forum/
LOCATION:Standard Brewing\, 2504 S Jackson St\, Seattle\, WA\, 98144\, United States
CATEGORIES:Electoral
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://seattledsa.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/EWG-logo-small-2.png
END:VEVENT
