SUMMARY:Know Your Rights Canvass
DESCRIPTION:In Seattle and across the country\, too many students and their families are afraid to be in public and to come to school. Some decide to self-deport. Immigration enforcement is violating and restricting our rights and creating a climate of fear. In Los Angeles\, Chicago\, and across the country\, educators have been on the frontline keeping their communities safe from ICE activities. \nSeattle Democratic Socialists of America\, educators\, and the broader community are also organizing to combat this violence and fear by forming rapid response networks\, distributing Know Your Rights information\, and more. Training and materials will be provided!
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/know-your-rights-canvass-2/
LOCATION:RSVP for details\, Seattle\, WA\, 98122\, United States
CATEGORIES:Electoral,Immigration Justice,New Member Friendly
GEO:47.6087583;-122.2964235
END:VEVENT
