UID:10018246-1773583200-1773590400@seattledsa.org
SUMMARY:Seattle Cuba Friendship Committee Informational Picket
DESCRIPTION:Our comrades with Seattle Cuba Friendship Committee are putting on an informational picket to draw attention to the deepening crisis in Cuba: \n“On January 29\, President Trump issued an Executive Order declaring a national emergency under the National Emergencies Act\, stating that “the policies\, practices\, and actions of the Government of Cuba constitute an unusual and extraordinary threat” to U.S. national security and foreign policy. This order intensified the blockade against Cuba to include a blockade of all oil shipments going to the island.\nTrump’s goal is to push Cuba to the edge of collapse.\nIn response\, we and other Cuba supporters around the world are mobilizing to protest the cruel and illegal blockade\, and encouraging our Congressional representatives to lift it.” \nJoin our DSA contingent at the rally to stand in solidarity with the Cuban people.
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/seattle-cuba-friendship-committee-informational-picket/
CATEGORIES:Anti-War / Anti-Imperialism,New Member Friendly
END:VEVENT
