SUMMARY:Universal Childcare: Next Steps
DESCRIPTION:Earlier this year\, Seattle DSA decided not to continue with its efforts to run a city-wide ballot initiative. This meeting is a continuation of conversations about how the chapter can continue organizing for universal childcare.
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/sdsa-universal-childcare-next-steps/
END:VEVENT
