SUMMARY:Ecosocialism and Green New Deal Working Group
DESCRIPTION:This week we are starting earlier and meeting in person in the U District for continued conversations about a shared vision for Ecosocialist politics in Seattle DSA.  Ahead of the meeting\, we have readings. “Manifesto for an Ecosocialist Revolution – Break with capitalist growth” provides a comprehensive global context for our conversation. Then\, a shorter read as an alternative\, or as an optional bonus: “Three Principles of Ecosocialist Politics” by Kai Heron. \nRSVP here ! Location is a 15 to 20 minute walk from either the Roosevelt or U-District light rail stations\, and will be emailed to RSVPs .  Any questions\, please contact greennewdeal@seattledsa.org .
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/ecosocialism-and-green-new-deal-working-group-26/
LOCATION:RSVP for details!\, Capitol Hill\, Seattle\, WA\, 98112\, United States
CATEGORIES:Ecosocialism,Green New Deal
GEO:47.6329523;-122.2891887
