SUMMARY:EWG March Monthly Meeting
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Electoral Working Group’s March monthly meeting! The agenda for this meeting includes deliberating the Jaelynn Scott endorsement request\, reviewing other relevant Convention items\, and more.\n\nThis edition will be on Zoom only. Once you RSVP\, you’ll be emailed a Zoom link. See you there!\n\nWant to stay involved in EWG organizing between monthly meetings? Sign up for EWG’s Google calendar by filling out THIS FORM! You will be added to our Google Group and will receive Google calendar invites for our recurring subcommittee meetings for Campaign Operations and Campaign Planning\, as well as important one-off events.
