SUMMARY:Socialist Soccer! - 10am to 12pm
DESCRIPTION:Come play soccer with fellow socialists! This is a fun\, enjoyable way to get outdoors\, exercise\, and meet friendly socialists as well as non-socialist soccer enthusiasts! \nAll genders and skill levels are welcome! Safety is our top priority. To participate you must abide by our norms and agreements to avoid injuries and help us take care of one another. \nJoin us at Brighton Playfield in South Seattle. Map: goo.gl/maps/c74cytjrRB1vpT7h7\nWe almost always play on the most southern edge of the field. \nWe confirm if we have enough players each Sunday on a socialist soccer Signal chat. To be added\, download the Signal app\, and email your phone number to tdupuis42@gmail.com with a request to be added. \nThe game is usually at 10 AM\, but that may change\, so make sure you are on the Socialist Soccer signal chat!
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/socialist-soccer-10am-to-12pm/2026-03-22/
LOCATION:Brighton Playfield\, 6000 39th Ave S\, Seattle\, WA\, 98118\, United States
CATEGORIES:New Member Friendly,Socials
GEO:47.5499039;-122.2810004
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Brighton Playfield 6000 39th Ave S Seattle WA 98118 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=6000 39th Ave S:geo:-122.2810004,47.5499039
END:VEVENT
