SUMMARY:Labor Organizing Happy Hour
DESCRIPTION:Workers and labor organizers from all over Seattle and King County get together\, hear the latest from the picket lines\, talk about labor organizing\, share struggles in our unions\, and get to know each other. All union activists\, socialists\, and community members are welcome to attend! \nAnyone is welcome whether you’re not a union member (yet)\, a long time union activist\, or anywhere in between. \nLook for our Labor Happy Hour posters on or near our table at Chuck’s Hop Shop \nRSVP Here
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/labor-organizing-happy-hour-14/
LOCATION:Chuck’s Hop Shop (Central District)\, 2001 E Union St\, Seattle\, WA\, 98122\, United States
CATEGORIES:Labor,New Member Friendly,Socials
