DESCRIPTION:Join us for the biweekly meeting of the Housing Justice Working Group! Free food and drinks will be provided. \nThe Housing Justice Working Group is committed to creating a Seattle without sweeps\, evictions\, or housing scarcity\, where housing is a human right and not a commodity. \nThe full agenda is available on Discord (check out the pinned comment in the housing-justice-general channel). If you aren’t part of the Discord yet\, members in good standing can join here.
